ResponseText: While liberals crusade against such terrifying things as evangelical music concerts in the military (oh the horror!), they continue to over-regulate in other areas too. Guitar Frets: Environmental Enforcement Leaves Musicians in Fear | Postmodern Times - WSJ.com Personally, I don't see how anybody can possibly question why the Obama administration is in so much trouble these days after reading things like this.

I doubt very much that the Obama administration had anything at all to do with this, other than enforcing environmental laws enacted in previous administrations. Obviously, you, Jyoshu, would have no problem at all with slaughtering all the remaining elephants in the world so that pianos could have genuine ivory keys.
Most musicians are out of touch with reality.
